Real README data to come!

For now, here's a peak at how this plugin could be used in a CFWheels application. 
The configuration (config/settings.cfm):
loc.flickr = {};
loc.flickr.flickrAPIKey = "MYKEY";
loc.flickr.flickrSecret = "MYSECRET";
loc.flickr.flickrURL = "http://api.flickr.com/services/rest/";
loc.flickr.flickrMethod = "flickr.photosets.getPhotos";
loc.flickr.flickrURLMethod = "get";
set(flickr=loc.flickr);

The controller:
function show(){
    link_name = reReplaceNoCase(trim(params.key),"\+"," ");
    destination = model("Destination").findOne(where="flash_link='#lcase(link_name)#'");
    $setSimpleFlickrConfig(argumentCollection=get("flickr"));
    if(trim(destination.flickr_set_id) != ""){
        try{
            slideshow = getFlickrPhotoSetPhotos(photosetID = destination.flickr_set_id);
            cachePut(destination.flickr_set_id,slideshow,createTimespan(30,0,0,0),createTimespan(14,0,0,0),"FlickrCache");
        }
        catch(Any e){
            slideshow = []
        }
    }
    if (!IsObject(destination)){
      flashInsert(error="Destination #params.key# was not found");
    }
}

The view: 
<cfoutput>
    <div id="slider">
        <cfloop array="#arguments.slideshow#" index="photo">
          #imageTag(source=photo.url, title=photo.title)#
        </cfloop>
    </div>
</cfoutput>